<br>
This would be similar to putting malo on a mob until someone can land a malosini on it.<br>
<br>
That would give people a reason to have beastlords on a raid without diminishing the role of shamans in the least.  If you gave shamans a lure slow then you're back to where we are now, with beastlords not having any ability that makes them an &quot;essential&quot; part of a raid force. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=90287 target=_blank><img src=http://www.tchalla.net/BenPortrait.jpg /></a><br>
